text: Did you know that there's a tour around the world? was the sixth headlining concert tour by American singer-songwriter Lana Del Rey, in support of her ninth studio album Did you know that there's a tunnel under ocean blvd. It began on May 27, 2023 at Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, and concluded on August 25, 2024 at Leeds, England. == Background == Lana Del Rey went on the Norman Fucking Rockwell! Tour in 2019. She got sick and could not finish the tour in 2020. Because of COVID-19, Del Rey could not tour until 2023. Her new tour was announced in early 2023. == Set list == These are the songs that Lana Del Rey sang in Quebec City, Canada.
